Package: bellreg
Title: Count Regression Models Based on the Bell Distribution
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Fabio", family = "Demarqui", email = "fndemarqui@est.ufmg.br", role = c("aut", "cre"),  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9236-1986")),
	         person(given = "Marcos", family = "Prates", role = "ctb",  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8077-4898")))
Description: Bell Regression models for count data with overdispersion. The implemented models account for ordinary and zero-inflated regression models under both frequentist and Bayesian approaches. Theorical details regarding the models implemented in the package can be found in Castellares et al. (2018) and Lemonte et al. (2020).
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/fndemarqui/bellreg
BugReports: https://github.com/fndemarqui/bellreg/issues
